description:
True Crime Tuesday presents Dumb Crimes & Stupid Criminals Choke, Chomp, Chew Edition!

Dave digs through the insanity of the past week in Dumb Crimes from around the world! Russian Cannibal Car Crash, Witness Protection or Witless Protection, an Emotional Support Cat owner takes her job seriously when it comes to taking care of her furry friend, Uber Drivers Beware of the Choke & Chomp rider, Police Car Sex, a streamer takes a shot to the junk AND more!
